    "summary": "In the millennial day all men will praise the Lord—He will dwell among them—Compare Isaiah 12. About 559–545 B.C.",
    "chapterAugmentations": [],
    "verses": [
      {
        "text": "And in that day thou shalt say: O Lord, I will praise thee; though thou wast angry with me thine anger is turned away, and thou comfortedst me.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "Isa. 12:1 (1–6).",
            "start": 0,
            "end": 3
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Behold, God is my salvation; I will trust, and not be afraid; for the Lord Jehovah is my strength and my song; he also has become my salvation.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "Ps. 36:7 (7–8); Mosiah 4:6; Hel. 12:1.",
            "start": 36,
            "end": 41
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Strength.",
            "start": 89,
            "end": 97
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Singing.",
            "start": 105,
            "end": 109
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Therefore, with joy shall ye draw water out of the wells of salvation.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "TG Living Water.",
            "start": 34,
            "end": 39
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "And in that day shall ye say: Praise the Lord, call upon his name, declare his doings among the people, make mention that his name is exalted.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "TG Praise; Thanksgiving.",
            "start": 30,
            "end": 36
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Sing unto the Lord; for he hath done excellent things; this is known in all the earth.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "Ps. 57:7 (7–11); 108:1 (1–5); Alma 26:8; D&C 136:28.",
            "start": 0,
            "end": 4
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Cry out and shout, thou inhabitant of Zion; for great is the Holy One of Israel in the midst of thee.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "Isa. 54:1 (1–8); Zeph. 3:14 (14–20); Zech. 2:10 (10–13).",
            "start": 0,
            "end": 3
